<constraints>
- Target 200-400 lines.
- Every API endpoint from technical.md must have at least one happy-path and one error-path test case.
- Acceptance criteria must map to user stories from product.md.
- Test framework must match what was detected in the brownfield scan.
- Coverage targets must be specific percentages, not ranges.
- Performance benchmarks must match or be more stringent than the targets in technical.md.
- Security checklist must reference specific OWASP items relevant to this feature.
- Deployment verification must be a runnable checklist (smoke tests, health checks, rollback steps).
- Do not repeat architecture or data model — reference technical.md for those details.
</constraints>

